    "We further discuss future directions and adjacent applications of topological deep learning, and we present some current libraries.",
    "Finally, we make some concluding remarks in Sect. 5.",
    "Notations We write X ∈ ℝ n×d to denote the data set, where n is the number of samples and d the number of features or dimensions.",
    "We write M to denote the underlying data manifold, which, for the purposes of this survey, is a locally Euclidean space embedded in ℝ d.",
    "We write BD and PD as abbreviations of barcode diagram and persistence diagram."
